Package com.github.wuic.path

This package defines the contracts and abstractions of those contracts of a little API designed by WUIC to resolve path navigation.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DirectoryPath This interface represents a path which is a directory.
DirectoryPathFactory Interface of object in charge of creating new DirectoryPath.
FilePath This interface represents a path which is a file.
Path A path is an element which is could be linked to another path as parent to represent a hierarchy.
 

Class Summary
AbstractDirectoryPath Abstract implementation of a DirectoryPath.
 

Package com.github.wuic.path Description

This package defines the contracts and abstractions of those contracts of a little API designed by WUIC to resolve path navigation.

Classes in this package don't throw WUIC exceptions like StreamException or BadArgumentException to ease the reuse of this code outside WUIC.
